snippet.title: Lets Play Brutal Mario World Part 1
snippet.description:
My first Let's Play is going to be Brutal Mario World

created by a Japanese Rom hacker named Carol

Proton Jon videos coming soon!
so brace yourself for them!

Levels:
Yoshi's House ~The most boring level in any hack!
Journey's Beginning~A normal stage with no gimmicks... that's one of the only stages that will be like that!
Journey's End~A level all about HDMA and random brothers.
Catch Yoshi~This level boggles my mind... A Fat Guy chasing a dinosaur across a sandy beach is hysterical!
Lively Water~Another HDMA level with hidden surprises everywhere!

Join My Website:
http://collabhack.ning.com/
